<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Anthonig<ex>en</ex></expan> vom <expan>Rotenhan<ex>n,</ex></expan>
<expan>dechand<ex>en</ex></expan> des stiffts czu
                            <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g,</expan> oder seinem official in
                                <expan>geistl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
